知识点。<br>                   比如，早上就是极客时间。<br>                   晚上是SLAM相关知识。<br>                   中午就是孩子教育相关的。<br><br>                    然后，到了那个时间点，自然就想学那个知识点了。能有利于长期坚持下去。别随意切知识点，切来切去，哪个知识点也没有坚持学下去。<br><br><br>困难2：学习方向不对，学了很多没用的。有用的却忽略掉了。<br>解决：<br>        1. 进行业社群，看人家聊什么，有什么文章，有什么书籍推荐。 找一个切入点，生往里切。<br>一个切入点切不进去，再找别的切入点，反正总能找到一个。然后，慢慢的就有点感觉了。<br>        2. B站很不错，有很多学习资料。找到切入点以后，去B站找找，往往能找到这个切入点上，更系统的公开课。能系统的学习一下。","like_count":10,"discussions":[{"author":{"id":1098920,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/10/c4/a8/f2685e1b.jpg","nickname":"华仔","note":"","ucode":"851FF94CF5133A","race_medal":0,"user_type":2,"is_pvip":false},"reply_author":{"id":0,"avatar":"","nickname":"","note":"","ucode":"","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":513042,"discussion_content":"困难2我建议还是多跟身边的同事中的高手请教，行业社群如果是微信群的话，效率不高，我现在基本都不怎么加群聊。\n\nB站很多视频资料确实不错。","likes_number":0,"is_delete":false,"is_hidden":false,"ctime":1609838273,"is_liked":false,"can_delete":false,"is_complain":false,"is_top":true,"parent_id":0,"ip_address":""},"score":2,"extra":"{\"reply\":true,\"user_type\":2}","child_discussion_number":0,"child_discussions":[]},{"author":{"id":1259488,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/13/37/e0/23f288ae.jpg","nickname":"周平","note":"","ucode":"4954DC474C4FDF","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"reply_author":{"id":0,"avatar":"","nickname":"","note":"","ucode":"","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":339956,"discussion_content":"明白了，谢谢导师","likes_number":0,"is_delete":false,"is_hidden":false,"ctime":1609848296,"is_liked":false,"can_delete":false,"is_complain":false,"is_top":false,"parent_id":0,"ip_address":""},"score":2,"extra":"","child_discussion_number":0,"child_discussions":[]}]},{"had_liked":false,"id":271651,"user_name":"金鹏","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1019485,"ip_address":"","ucode":"916180E1699264","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/0f